code: @Override public void join(Tuple2<String, String> first, Tuple2<String, Integer> second, Collector<Tuple4<String, String, String, Object>> out) throws Exception {     if (first == null) {         out.collect(new Tuple4<String, String, String, Object>(null, null, second.f0, second.f1)).     } else if (second == null) {         out.collect(new Tuple4<String, String, String, Object>(first.f0, first.f1, null, null)).     } else {         out.collect(new Tuple4<String, String, String, Object>(first.f0, first.f1, second.f0, second.f1)).     } }
